{"tid":1055614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［高度致敬］華為honor FlyPods真無線耳機","createTime":"2019-03-10T16:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T17:31:45.000Z","uid":2104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f57ca2b604f6725220bf65feb426c9d8cb86f33","tid":1055614,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHHEwCn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHHEwCn.png&h=0585d28d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前陣子認識了一位3C同好，跟我的個性很像，對3C資訊產品非常熱愛，手機，週邊，筆電，這些他都很愛體驗各種最新的科技，所以在一次的聚會，他秀給我看一組華為推出的真無線藍牙耳機，看我感到極高興趣時，他也很大方的說，你那麼喜歡就借去用用吧。於是，這個勸敗的動作造成了今天我這篇的開箱，honor FlyPods，紅色版！<br />\n<br />\n在中國大陸，honor榮耀品牌是華為推出的平價3C副品牌，就像小米旗下的&quot;紅米Red Mi&quot;，honor出品的手機跟配件在台灣目前尚未引進，所以要買到要自行去中國大陸當地購買或是透過水貨店家購入。第一眼看到honor FlyPods，直覺就是 嗯哼就很明顯的學蘋果apple的AirPods啊，外型像，一樣白色，功能也幾乎一樣，主打真無線耳機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bi2UkvM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBi2UkvM.png&h=e84f1435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這種非完全入耳式的耳機，音效我個人覺得還是稍微差耳塞式耳機一點，不過也有個好處就是戴這個耳機還是能夠聽到大部份的周遭聲音，因此走在馬路上還是能夠清楚聽到車聲跟喇叭聲，讓你更能掌握環境的潛在危險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9VZwCC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9VZwCC.png&h=3c5d71bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶上去的樣子，嗯，就跟AirPods一樣像是EarPods被剪掉線的樣子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ur0F0v6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUr0F0v6.png&h=d31f57cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFlyPods沒有任何按鍵，但是它支援敲兩下的動作，右邊耳機敲2下可以播放/暫停音樂，左邊耳機敲2下可直接免解鎖啟動手機的Google助理功能，非常方便<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpkbnKO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpkbnKO.png&h=55c74fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFlyPods跟AirPods一樣有個專屬收納盒子，同時也是個專屬的充電座<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayfZwDo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FayfZwDo.png&h=c7ce9640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n充電盒後面有一個按鍵，是讓你可以快速查看FlyPods的電力狀況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QbJYiz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QbJYiz.png&h=d7f4f9e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFlyPods收納盒底下的充電孔是Type C孔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UegNFxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUegNFxb.png&h=0ab276f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFlyPods比AirPods還要再帥氣的地方就是它支援無線充電<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dG289qF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdG289qF.png&h=8bdb9ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7087/3658821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7087%2F3658821&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=431759ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7087/3658821</a><br />\n<br />\n華為如果無咗蘋果真係會冇晒靈感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a011c864f86c4f56e1b4aab2141377efba2430ab","tid":1055614,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾臺狗撚無恥照抄都做工商"},{"pid":"421c338b057b1dd047229b28e894065f7cd21978","tid":1055614,"uid":192571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"屌 淨係見華為間鋪個格局一早就係啦"}]}